text: Sphaerium rhomboideum, the rhomboid fingernailclam, is a species of freshwater clams in the family Sphaeriidae. It is found in North America. == References == == External links == * * Sphaerium rhomboideum at mussel-project.uwsp.edu rhomboideum Category:Bivalves described in 1822
title: Sphaerium rhomboideum
